      "rationale": "k-ω SST turbulence closure selected based on literature consensus for rotating internal flows. Power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen et al.) is industry standard. Formal model-form uncertainty quantification deferred per MRL 2 scoping; assumptions documented in simulation plan."
